                            <h2 class="SWWW_H2">Our Mission and Vision</h2>
                            <p class="SWWW_P">Sustainable WWW was founded in 2021 by Max and Michael Andersen with a clear mission – to reduce the internet’s environmental impact. It all began as a blog where we shared our research and practical advice on how web development could become more sustainable.</p>
                            <p class="SWWW_P">The blog quickly grew, inspiring web developers worldwide, leading to Sustainable WWW becoming an international company today, helping clients in Sweden, Denmark, Norway, and English-speaking countries create sustainable websites. Our mission remains the same – to make the internet more optimized, sustainable, and inclusive for a better future.</p>
                            <p class="SWWW_P">We ensure your websites and web applications meet your goals and requirements while ensuring a positive impact on the environment and your digital presence.</p>
                        </div>
