                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <p class="SWWW_P P--MaxWidth900"><strong>2022:</strong> The project evolved into a podcast, inspiring hundreds of developers and organizations to reduce their websites’ and web applications’ environmental impact.</p>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <p class="SWWW_P P--MaxWidth900"><strong>2023:</strong> We launched our first services, focusing on web design and optimization, and established partnerships with Scandinavian companies to create sustainable web solutions.</p>
                                </li>
                                <li>
